reviewText: What more is there to say?  It's the 2008 IOM and done up correctly, as usual, by Duke.  They specialize in this type of thing and if you're really into it, this is the way to go.  Of course by now (2013) you probably really don't care about the 2008 race but some guys like to keep a record of each year and if you missed 2008, this would be the way to update your library.
